{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1966,"month":9,"day":27}],"page_start":4,"page_end":4,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"太阳就是毛泽东","authors":["韩培梅"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"人如海，旗如林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万众仰望天安门。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天安门上太阳红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳就是毛泽东。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的心呵难平静，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好似大海波浪滚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲眼看见了毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我幸福的热泪眼眶里涌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席呀毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们最最热爱您，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高呼：“万岁！万万岁！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劲松翠柏万年青。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席呀爱我们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远站在群众中。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓝天当做一张纸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席的关怀写不尽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望着毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浑身都是劲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一辈子跟着您干革命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粉身碎骨不变心。"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}